Grammar

    0 $accept: function $end

    1 function: function_header variables body ';'

    2 function_header: FUNCTION IDENTIFIER optional_parameters RETURNS type ';'

    3 optional_parameters: parameters
    4                    | %empty

    5 parameters: parameters ',' parameter
    6           | parameter

    7 parameter: IDENTIFIER ':' type

    8 variables: variables variable
    9          | %empty

   10 variable: IDENTIFIER ':' type IS statement_
   11         | IDENTIFIER ':' LIST OF type IS list ';'

   12 type: INTEGER
   13     | REAL
   14     | CHARACTER

   15 list: '(' expressions ')'

   16 expressions: expressions ',' expression
   17            | expression

   18 body: BEGIN_ statement_ END

   19 statement_: statement ';'
   20           | error ';'

   21 statement: expression
   22          | WHEN condition ',' expression ':' expression

   23 $@1: %empty

   24 statement: SWITCH expression IS $@1 cases OTHERS ARROW statement_ ENDSWITCH
   25          | IF condition THEN statement_ elsif_clauses ELSE statement_ ENDIF
   26          | FOLD direction operator list_choice ENDFOLD

   27 elsif_clauses: elsif_clauses ELSIF condition THEN statement_
   28              | %empty

   29 cases: cases case
   30      | %empty

   31 case: CASE INT_LITERAL ARROW statement_

   32 direction: LEFT
   33          | RIGHT

   34 operator: ADDOP
   35         | MULOP
   36         | MODOP
   37         | EXPOP

   38 list_choice: list
   39            | IDENTIFIER

   40 condition: or_condition

   41 or_condition: or_condition OROP and_condition
   42             | and_condition

   43 and_condition: and_condition ANDOP not_condition
   44              | not_condition

   45 not_condition: NOTOP not_condition
   46              | relation

   47 relation: '(' condition ')'
   48         | expression RELOP expression

   49 expression: expression ADDOP term
   50           | term

   51 term: term MULOP power
   52     | term MODOP power
   53     | power

   54 power: unary EXPOP power
   55      | unary

   56 unary: NEGOP unary
   57      | primary

   58 primary: '(' expression ')'
   59        | INT_LITERAL
   60        | REAL_LITERAL
   61        | CHAR_LITERAL
   62        | IDENTIFIER '(' expression ')'
   63        | IDENTIFIER


Terminals, with rules where they appear

    $end (0) 0
    '(' (40) 15 47 58 62
    ')' (41) 15 47 58 62
    ',' (44) 5 16 22
    ':' (58) 7 10 11 22
    ';' (59) 1 2 11 19 20
    error (256) 20
    IDENTIFIER <iden> (258) 2 7 10 11 39 62 63
    INT_LITERAL <value> (259) 31 59
    REAL_LITERAL <value> (260) 60
    CHAR_LITERAL <value> (261) 61
    ADDOP <oper> (262) 34 49
